- File-length optimization beyond the SKILL.md split was not pursued — user explicitly deferred further skill optimization for separate work.

## Context
Designed and implemented the `shipping-pr` skill plus its `/skill-set:pr:ship` slash command, completing the PR-lifecycle gap between `git:pr` (create only) and `pr:fix` (one-shot blocker resolution). Iteratively refined via parallel peer LLM review (Gemini, Codex, Claude); fixed 3 critical bugs and applied 4 of 5 ambiguous recommendations per user direction. Final structure: `SKILL.md` (168 lines) + `reference/{polling,blocker-resolution,troubleshooting}.md`, fully passing `creating-skills` guardrails. Plugin auto-discovery means no `plugin.json`/`marketplace.json` edits were needed.

